Package de.fhb.sailboat.gui.map

Provides the classes necessary to use and work with the map in the graphic user interface.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
MapPolygon Interface for Polygons.
 

Class Summary
DefaultMapController Default map controller which implements map moving by pressing the right mouse button and zooming by double click or by mouse wheel.
GeneralMap Class for dividing between a map for representing in the GUI and a map recognizing the interactions with it.
GUIMap Class for dividing between a map for representing in the GUI and a map recognizing the interactions with it.
Map Primary Map-class which uses all the other classes.
MapMarkerDot A simple implementation of the MapMarker interface.
MapPolygonImpl Class which represents a polygon as a list and drawable on the map.
MapRectangleImpl Class which represents a rectangle which can be displayed on the map.
MissionCreatingMap Class for dividing between a map for representing in the GUI and a map recognizing the interactions with it.
